* suckless st terminal
https://st.suckless.org
mkdir some/suitable/directory
git clone git://git.suckless.org/st
apt install pkg-config libfontconfig1-dev xorg-dev
update config.h as required (increase font size)
e.g. char font[] = "Ubuntu Mono:style=Regular:pixelsize=16:antialias=true:autohint=true";
sudo make clean install
